languages.en_GB: &7Started parkour! Try to beat your high-score of &c%1&7!
languages.ro_RO: &7Ai inceput parcursul de parkour! incearca sa iti depasesti scorul maxim de &c%1&7!

languages.en_GB: &7No arena or player could be found called &c%1&7!
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu s-a putut gasi o arena sau un jucator cu numele &c%1&7!
&7L-ai forat pe &c%1&7 sa faca parkour in zona &c%2&7!

languages.en_GB: &7You do not have permission to do that!
&4&lCongrats!&7 You beat your previous score of &c%1&7!
languages.ro_RO: &4&lFelicitari!&7 Ai depasit scorul tau anterior de &c%1&7!

languages.en_GB: &4&lCongrats! &7You just beat your previous highscore! Keep going!
languages.ro_RO: &4&lFelicitari! &7Ai depasit scorul tau maxim anterior! Continua in acelasi ritm!

languages.en_GB: &7You cannot start parkour from this world!
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu poti incepe parcursul de parkour din aceasta lume!
&7Aceasta nu este o valoare numerica valida!

languages.en_GB: C&7ould not start parkour because the area is full! Try again later.
languages.ro_RO: N&7u s-a putut incepe parcursul de parkour deoarece zona este plina! incearca din nou mai tarziu.

languages.en_GB: &7You must be in-game to do that!
languages.ro_RO: &7Trebuie sa fii in joc pentru a face asta!

languages.en_GB: &7You must do this command from the console!
languages.ro_RO: &7Trebuie sa folosesti aceasta comanda din consola!
&7Nimeni nu a jucat parcursul de parkour inca!

languages.en_GB: &7You can now do &c/ajParjour start &7to do parkour!
languages.ro_RO: &7Acum poti folosi &c/ajParjour start&7 pentru a incepe parcursul de parkour!
&7Jocul tau de parkour s-a incheiat deoarece

languages.en_GB: &7For info on how to set it up, do &c/%1 setup
languages.ro_RO: &7Pentru informatii despre cum sa-l setezi, foloseste &c/%1 setup

languages.en_GB: &7There are too many players in parkour right now. Try again later.
languages.ro_RO: &7Sunt prea multi jucatori in parcursul de parkour acum. incearca din nou mai tarziu.

languages.en_GB: &7Please provide the source to migrate from!
languages.ro_RO: &7Te rog ofera sursa de la care sa migrezi!

languages.en_GB: &7Something went wrong. There is probably more information in the console.
languages.ro_RO: &7Ceva nu a mers bine. Probabil exista mai multe informatii in consola.

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 start <area> &7- Start parkour in a certain area.
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 start <zona> &7- incepe parcursul de parkour intr-o anumita zona.

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 start <player> [area] &7- Start another players parkour in a certain area.
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 start <jucator> [zona] &7- incepe parcursul de parkour al altui jucator intr-o anumita zona.

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 list &7- See everyone that is playing parkour, and their current scores.
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 list &7- Vezi toti cei care joaca parcursul de parkour, si scorurile lor actuale.

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 setup &7- Commands for setting up the plugin. (required permssion: &cajparkour.setup&7)
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup &7- Comenzi pentru setarea pluginului. (permisiune necesara: &cajparkour.setup&7)

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 portals &7- Commands for setting up portals.
&c/%1 setup pos1 &7- Set the first position
&c/%1 setup pos2 &7- Set the second position
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup pos2 &7- Seteaza a doua pozitie

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 setup we &7- Select first and second position with worldedit
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup we &7- Selecteaza prima si a doua pozitie cu worldedit
&c/%1 setup fallpos &7- Seteaza pozitia de cadere!

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 edit&7 - Load an existing area into the editing queue.
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 edit&7 - incarca o zona existenta in coada de editare.

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 setup info&7 - Show which points you have set so far!
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup info&7 - Arata ce puncte ai setat pana acum!

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 setup difficulty &7- Set the areas difficulty!
&c/%1 setup max &7- Set the maximum number of people allowed in the area!
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup max &7- Seteaza numarul maxim de persoane permise in zona!

languages.en_GB: &c/%1 setup save &7- Saves and enabled the area. (This should be done last)
languages.ro_RO: &c/%1 setup save &7- Salveaza si activeaza zona. (Asta ar trebui sa fie facut ultimul)

languages.en_GB: &7You cannot use this command while on parkour!
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu poti folosi aceasta comanda cand esti in parcursul de parkour!

languages.en_GB: &7You cannot run this command from the console!
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu poti folosi aceasta comanda din consola!

languages.en_GB: &7You are not allowed to name your arena like that.
&7Please enter the name of an area to edit!
languages.ro_RO: &7Te rog introdu numele unei zone de editat!

languages.en_GB: &7Area loaded for editing! Re-set positions using &c/%1 setup
languages.ro_RO: &7Zona incarcata pentru editare! Reseteaza pozitiile folosind &c/%1 setup

languages.en_GB: &7An area with that name does not exist!
languages.ro_RO: &7O zona cu acel nume nu exista!

languages.en_GB: &7You must create an area before editing it!
languages.ro_RO: &7Trebuie sa creezi o zona inainte de a o edita!

languages.en_GB: &7You need to have WorldEdit installed to use this command! Try using the built-in pos1 and pos2 setup commands.
languages.ro_RO: &7Trebuie sa ai WorldEdit instalat pentru a folosi aceasta comanda! incearca sa folosesti comenzile incorporate pos1 si pos2.

languages.en_GB: &7You must make a complete worldedit selection before doing this!
languages.ro_RO: &7Trebuie sa faci o selectie completa a WorldEdit inainte de a face asta!

languages.en_GB: &7Area created and added to the editing queue. See &c/ajParkour setup&7 or view the plugin page for steps to set it up!
languages.ro_RO: &7Zona creata si adaugata in coada de editare. Vezi &c/ajParkour setup&7 sau viziteaza pagina pluginului pentru pasii de setare!

languages.en_GB: &7An arena is currently being set up. Please either save that arena, or run this command again to override. (&cNOTE: Overriding will erase all of the data of the arena being set up before!&7)
languages.ro_RO: &7O arena este setata in prezent. Te rog fie salveaza acea arena, fie ruleaza aceasta comanda din nou pentru a o suprascrie. (&cNOTA: Suprascrierea va sterge toate datele arenei care este setata inainte!&7)

languages.en_GB:
&7Please enter a difficulty! Valid difficulties are easy, medium, hard, expert, and balanced.
Balanced difficulty will make the parkour get harder as the player gets higher scores.
languages.ro_RO:
&7Te rog introdu o dificultate! Dificultatile valide sunt easy, medium, hard, expert, si balanced.
Dificultatea echilibrata va face parcursul sa devina mai dificil pe masura ce jucatorul obtine scoruri mai mari.

languages.en_GB: &7You have not set all of the required settings! Check &c/%1 setup info&7 to see what you have left.
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu ai setat toate setarile necesare! Verifica &c/%1 setup info&7 pentru a vedea ce ti-a ramas.

languages.en_GB:
&7The area you just created does not meet the minimum reccomended size of &c20x20x20!&7
You can continue creating the area, but know you may run into issues with players running into each other, and possibly parkour going outside the area!
Your area: &c%1x%2x%3&7 (&cXxZxY&7)
languages.ro_RO:
&7Zona pe care tocmai ai creat-o nu indeplineste dimensiunea minima recomandata de &c20x20x20!&7
Poti continua crearea zonei, dar stii ca ai putea intampina probleme cu jucatorii care se lovesc unul de altul, si posibil parcursul sa iasa din zona!
Zona ta: &c%1x%2x%3&7 (&cXxZxY&7)

languages.en_GB: &7Created a portal named &c%1&7 at your current location! You might have to restart the server for the portal to start working.
languages.ro_RO: &7Creat un portal numit &c%1&7 la locatia ta curenta! S-ar putea sa trebuiasca sa repornesti serverul pentru ca portalul sa inceapa sa functioneze.

languages.en_GB: &7Please enter the name of the portal to be removed!
languages.ro_RO: &7Te rog introdu numele portalului de eliminat!

languages.en_GB: &7Cannot find a portal with that name! Make sure you spelled it correctly, and that you put the same caps too.
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu s-a putut gasi un portal cu acel nume! Asigura-te ca l-ai scris corect, si ca ai pus aceleasi litere mari si mici.

languages.en_GB: &7No portals have been set up yet! Please create portals before removing them.
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu s-au setat portaluri inca! Te rog creeaza portaluri inainte de a le elimina.

languages.en_GB: &7Please enter the name of the area to be removed!
languages.ro_RO: &7Te rog introdu numele zonei de eliminat!

languages.en_GB: &7Cannot find an area with that name! Make sure you spelled it correctly, and that you put the same caps too.
languages.ro_RO: &7Nu s-a putut gasi o zona cu acel nume! Asigura-te ca l-ai scris corect, si ca ai pus aceleasi litere mari si mici.
